{"tid":1189152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反逃犯條例修訂]政府醫生協會長：公僕也不能埋沒良知","createTime":"2019-06-06T16:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T23:27:55.000Z","uid":38842,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d4352c267ad9c4f9bad6b3e4cc7a61c43343f380","tid":1189152,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"【引渡惡法】醫學界議員陳沛然表態反修例 籲醫生周日齊上街<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190606&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59686301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190606%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59686301&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=4f78e87b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190606%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59686301&h=620fb6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190606&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59686301</a><br />\n<br />\n醫學界早前就反對《逃犯條例》修例發起聯署，但身為醫學界立法會議員的陳沛然，卻遲遲未有公開表態。「反惡法」遊行將於3日後舉行，陳終於指自己立場明確反對修例，更會遊行，並呼籲業界參加。他解釋，當日下午3時需到元朗出席立法會足球隊活動，因早已答應出席，不得不去，但在活動之後，再參加遊行。他指，為免大眾誤會他當日不參加反惡法遊行，加上業界對自己的取態感興趣，為免大家「估估吓」，決定公開自己當日的行程。<br />\n<br />\n公營醫療醫生協會與政府醫生協會舉行周年晚宴。出席晚宴的陳沛然，被記者問到為何其反修例的取態一直低調，陳解釋，自己毋須成為領頭反對修例的人物，其當日的行程之前一直只在私人facebook賬號公開。在場記者隨即詢問，如今他公開行程，是否想呼籲醫學界參加遊行，陳則回答「算係」，但他笑言，自己是否呼籲業界參與，並非重要問題，「我又唔會擔住支旗行」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府醫生協會長：公僕也不能埋沒良知<br />\n<br />\n政府醫生協會會長李慧茵在致辭時表示，公院醫生向來緊守崗位，甚至在2003年面對沙士疫情時，都沒有「逃兵」。她談及近月醫委會通過海外醫生免實習的安排，呼籲曾離港工作的醫生返港，利用豐富的臨床經驗，重投本港公營醫療。李其後突然表示，做公院醫生都要保留個人意志，「做公務員唔係要將良知掉落垃圾桶」，但不願明言所指何事，僅稱「聰明嘅人就會知道」。她又指，會以個人名義參加反惡法遊行，私下亦有呼籲同僚和協會成員出席。</span>"},{"pid":"5b60ff61b2799b6f6e11eb41af1c89e135d24e21","tid":1189152,"uid":38842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327961339dc860964e5dbcae61be665285a381a4","tid":1189152,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d657deee9cd73aeec0d25b4fc6dcce4dc7fdcd6e","tid":1189152,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37938e1ea6d950e07e985ae5f33cc9a8f981fe51","tid":1189152,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54b76e245ad6535406b676380db8c4fd2634f0f","tid":1189152,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c71dd36c9bcf40b9dab6581dc7e328a4d0c279","tid":1189152,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"你地醫生有個專業牌梗係唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf0b3299f4dabe22e0f6ec274d91584705820b0","tid":1189152,"uid":38842,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e2c71dd36c9bcf40b9dab6581dc7e328a4d0c279","tid":1189152,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"你地醫生有個專業牌梗係唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更加要出黎發聲。<br />\n<br />\n但係都睇到點解政府越來越睇醫學界唔順眼。"},{"pid":"31583fdf3cc032b624b498cc36c2233f7aadacd6","tid":1189152,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"損害自身私益咪突然有良知囉"},{"pid":"41693b4232b402a09c4662b453de7572953c1dcb","tid":1189152,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9e070b614a41e72b28633daa94cf9700741cae","tid":1189152,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"守護香港 人人有責<br />\n<br />\n為保持紀律部隊在市民心中正面形象 減少害群之馬 請市民拍下所有\t違反人權之情況 影片需有1.狗牌號碼 2.猙獰狗樣 3.違反人權過程 eg打手無寸鐵嘅學生 （就算頭2樣冇都冇問題）<br />\n<br />\n影片請不要於社交媒體發佈<br />\n<br />\n待一同整理後 影片及有關資料 將發送盟國內政部 以便日後 違權者及其老婆子女 於歐美人權法案下 永續中國人身份 今生永久禁止入境歐美日等國家 及打擊資產向外移 與子孫共享中國人榮耀<br />\n<br />\n利申 支持政府執法 我愛毛主席 不鼓吹任何暴力行為"},{"pid":"b5114102f81c213a09c0807e85431ea24f5f9cb5","tid":1189152,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843d5861019444ee1133b47dc89cc6f7cc5481b4","tid":1189152,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmY1Du8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmY1Du8.jpg&h=6ddcf26c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e27733f064aae271542433da126f182a98faadb6","tid":1189152,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"天時地利人和俱備，今次一定眾志成城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7521f81e59b471a73df1666d49c4164f291a4b4","tid":1189152,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e27733f064aae271542433da126f182a98faadb6","tid":1189152,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"天時地利人和俱備，今次一定眾志成城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a65588b005a47a0367c35740fc06bf3d05a307",